{"tid":1265872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］4.7萬選民無覆掛號信取消資格　政黨﹕或「殺錯良民」","createTime":"2019-06-29T11:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T11:51:47.000Z","uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96a10a9795a9c66d42bfbce1885077d201cb8dc5","tid":1265872,"uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2015年9月1日星期二</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日有報章報導，選舉事務處早前以掛號信方式抽查全港已登記選民的住址，結果有約4.7萬個登記未在限期前回覆，被取消選民資格，不能在今年區議會選舉中投票。報導稱被取消登記當中以觀塘區佔最多，有逾8000多個登記被取消。<br />\n<br />\n身兼葵青區議員的民主黨副主席尹兆堅今早接受港台節目訪問時說，選舉事務處只向懷疑個案發掛號信查詢，有機會「殺錯良民」，他估計部分收信者可能是舊區長者，收了信亦不知何事而未有理會。他又指這個查核方法亦對意圖種票者沒阻嚇力，即使被抽中，種票者亦可回覆了事。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會黨團召集人葉國謙受訪時亦稱，選舉權是香港市民最重要的人權之一，若選舉事務處只以掛號信形式抽查，市民可能因各種原因收不到，認為該處應增加資源，直接接觸懷疑個案，以上門或電話方式核實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20150901/s00001/1441085838149/4-7%E8%90%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%86%E6%8E%9B%E8%99%9F%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8-%E6%88%96%E3%80%8C%E6%AE%BA%E9%8C%AF%E8%89%AF%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20150901%2Fs00001%2F1441085838149%2F4-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%258E%259B%25E8%2599%259F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E6%2588%2596%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%2589%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E3%2580%258D&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=74457f63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20150901%2Fs00001%2F1441085838149%2F4-7%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%258E%259B%25E8%2599%259F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E6%2588%2596%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%2589%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E3%2580%258D&h=1804e01a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20150901/s00001/1441085838149/4-7%E8%90%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%86%E6%8E%9B%E8%99%9F%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8-%E6%88%96%E3%80%8C%E6%AE%BA%E9%8C%AF%E8%89%AF%E6%B0%91%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n收到信記得一定要回信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db5a994a180d2957024d72b76864f8678a680c5","tid":1265872,"uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}